txt.en: Defeat the Champion of Mokh Shapat ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Mokh Shapat can be found in Arandor.\n\nYou should defeat the champion of Mokh Shapat and the encampment's raiders.
Defeated the Champion of Mokh Shapat ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Mokh Shapat can be found in Arandor.\n\nYou should defeat the champion of Mokh Shapat and the encampment's raiders.
The bellowing voice of Mokh Shapat's champion echoes across the encampment as he orders the raiders under his command to descend upon Díngarth. Both raiders and champion must be stopped.
The champion of Mokh Shapat has been silenced, and his raiders will no longer menace Díngarth or Adambel.
Defeated many foes at Mokh Shapat.
Many Orcs and beasts under the command of Sauron gather at the encampment of Mokh Shapat.
